<p><strong>Jack Bright在此安息</strong></p>
<p><strong>发布时间：</strong>2020年6月4日</p>
<p><strong>作者：</strong><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/lyrics-linn" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3935168); return false;"><img class="small" src="https://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3935168&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1603636327" alt="Lyrics Linn" style="background-image:url(https://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3935168)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/lyrics-linn" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3935168); return false;">Lyrics Linn</a></span>，进入<a href="/lyricslinn-s-personnel-file">人事档案</a>查看该名作者的更多作品</p>
<p>文中有许多隐藏链接，关于部分角色的相关故事。</p>
<p><strong>翻译：</strong><a href="http://scp-int.wikidot.com/jack-bright-resting-at-last">点此查看国际站发布版</a>，感谢<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/jochoi" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4255421); return false;"><img class="small" src="https://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4255421&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1603636327" alt="Jochoi" style="background-image:url(https://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4255421)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/jochoi" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4255421); return false;">Jochoi</a></span>的翻译！</p>
